WEBVTT

1
00:26:01.980 --> 00:26:03.750 
你会说十九种语言
You speak 19 languages.

2
00:26:03.850 --> 00:26:07.190 
偶尔用它们聊聊天总可以吧
You must occasionally use some of them to talk about things.

3
00:26:07.290 --> 00:26:10.520 
你们俩 总是待在一起
You two, you spend a great deal of time together.

4
00:26:10.630 --> 00:26:13.790 
我不在的话 你们会聊什么？
What would you be talking about if I weren't here?

5
00:26:14.860 --> 00:26:16.830 
巡逻
Patrol.

6
00:26:16.930 --> 00:26:19.570 
聊我带领无垢者一起巡逻的事
When I am going on patrol with the Unsullied.

7
00:26:19.670 --> 00:26:22.240 
我们巡逻时看到了什么
What we see on patrol.

8
00:26:22.340 --> 00:26:24.270 
巡逻时抓住了谁
Who we captured on patrol.

9
00:26:24.370 --> 00:26:26.840 
很好 非常好
That's good. That's very good.

10
00:26:28.940 --> 00:26:31.340 
但这只是报告
But that's a report.

